text: The Day the Fish Came Out is a 1967 Greek British comedy movie directed by Michael Cacoyannis and starring Tom Courtenay, Colin Blakely, Sam Wanamaker, Candice Bergen, Ian Ogilvy, Dimitris Nikolaidis. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. == Other websites == * * * * Category:1967 comedy movies Category:Greek movies Category:British comedy movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Michael Cacoyannis
